data.description: Save thousands of dollars a month with this 3.25% assumable VA mortgage and buy with ROAM. Come see this beautifully renovated all-brick home with a fully finished basement nestled in the sought-after Belvedere Park. NO HOA! Short drive to downtown Decatur, the Beltline, Shoal Creek Park, and shopping at Madison Yards. The open-concept floorplan features stunning hardwood flooring throughout with all new systems (Roof, HVAC, and Water Heater). As you enter the home, the spacious dining room is situated off the kitchen and perfect for entertaining groups of guests, both large and small. The impressive kitchen features an abundance of cabinetry with stone countertops, stainless steel kitchen appliances, and a large breakfast bar. The cozy family room includes modern touches with a unique wall-hanging home office space overlooking the large rear deck and private fenced backyard. The main level owner’s suite includes vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet, and a private bathroom with dual vanities and a glass-framed tiled shower. There are also two secondary bedrooms, a hall bathroom, and a laundry area on the main floor. The finished terrace level includes a guest bedroom full bathroom, and a spacious living/game room area with hardwood flooring, a large TV wall divider, and tons of storage space. Ideal for an in-law suite or Airbnb rental with its own private entrance. There is ample parking on the large level driveway. This home is perfectly situated near schools, parks, shopping, MARTA, and all major highways.
